Full and more detailed release notes are always available at the GitHub repository!

v0.19.3

* Timeline: local points now connect seamlessly to the synced API track
* Timeline: distance filter is now a configurable per-user preference
* Timeline: current-location marker hidden on historical date views
* Stats: cached stats are preserved when a refresh fails while offline
* Auth: QR code scanner available on hosted/cloud login screen
* Onboarding: permissions page can now be skipped without granting all permissions
* Self-signed certificate support via native HTTP client
* Batch upload expiration: stale uploads are automatically cleaned up
* Auto mode (GPS stream) is now the default tracking mode for new installs
